      ~#appenddesc[cAPaFiendW,"{b}Way of the Wicked{/b} A lawful evil anti-paladin may not use their fiendish boon to add the 'anarchic' property to a weapon. Instead, they may add the 'axiomatic' property."]]]></eval>
