  <thing id="arWoWUnBar" name="Unholy Barrister" description="Wretched are the clerics that worship Asmodeus, but there are some among them that truly find a calling in the service of the unholy lord. These clerics, known as unholy barristers, are among the devil&apos;s most powerful servants in the lands of the living, tirelessly working to enslave all who dare to oppose him.{br}{br}{b}Deity{/b}: The cleric must worship Asmodeus.{br}{br}{b}Domains{/b}: The cleric must have the Evil or Law domain" compset="ClassVary" uniqueness="unique">
