  <thing id="ioWoWGrSpB" name="I, Having Roamed Beyond the Wall of Death (Level 18 Necromancer)" description="{i}This is not a single spellbook but three heavy, cracked and worn leatherbound volumes tied together by a leather belt. The three volumes have no formal title, though all are marked with an ornate G.S. monogram. Instead the title comes from the first sentence upon the first page which is written boldy and largely before the work descends into hundreds of pages of rambling, mad, tiny script.{/i}\n\n{b}Value{/b} 19,320 gp {b}Blank Pages{/b} 4\n\n{b}SPELLS{/b} \n9th - Conjuration: {i}teleportation circle{/i}, Necromancy: {i}energy drain, wail of the banshee;{/i} Universal: {i}wish{/i} \n8th - Abjuration: {i}prismatic wall{/i}; Conjuration: {i}incendiary cloud, rift of ruin{/i}; Necromancy: {i}create greater undead, horrid wilting, orb of the void, symbol of death{/i} \n7th - Conjuration: {i}caustic eruption, greater teleport;{/i} Evocation: {i}forcecage, mage&apos;s sword{/i}; Necromancy: {i}control undead{/i}, {i}finger of death, plague storm, waves of exhaustion;{/i} Transmutation: {i}greater age resistance{/i} \n6th - Abjuration: {i}greater dispel magic{/i}; Conjuration: {i}acid fog;{/i} Divination: {i}true seeing;{/i} Necromancy: {i}circle of death, create undead, symbol of fear, undeath to death;{/i} Transmutation: {i}age resistance{/i} \n5th - Conjuration: {i}acid spray, cloudkilll, wall of stone;{/i} Enchantment: {i}Feeblemind;{/i} Necromancy: {i}suffocation, symbol of pain;{/i} Transmutation: {i}Baleful Polymorph;{/i} Universal: {i}permanency{/i} \n4th - Conjuration: {i}black tentacles, dimension door;{/i} Divination: {i}detect scrying,{/i} Necromancy: {i}animate dead, bestow curse{/i}, {i}enervation, fear, greater false life{/i} \n3rd - Conjuration: {i}stinking cloud;{/i} Necromancy: {i}healing thief{/i}, {i}ray of exhaustion;{/i} Transmutation: {i}fly, haste{/i} \n2nd - Abjuration: {i}resist energy{/i}; Conjuration: {i}acid arrow, web;{/i} Necromancy: {i}blindness/deafness, ghoul touch, scare, spectral hand;{/i} Illusion: magic mouth, {i}mirror image{/i} \n1st - Abjuration: {i}alarm, endure elements, protection from good, shield;{/i} Conjuration: {i}mage armor, mount;{/i} Divination: {i}comprehend languages, identify;{/i} Necromancy: {i}ray of enfeeblement, ray of sickening, restore corpse, sculpt corpse;{/i} Transmutation: {i}expeditious retreat{/i}\n0th - all cantrips in the Pathfinder Roleplaying Game Core Rulebook save for those of the evocation and illusion schools." compset="Wondrous" uniqueness="unique">
