  <thing id="ioWoWVeBea" name="Veil of the Beating Heart" description="With this seemingly normal veil of black cloth, you may change yourself physically (as with {i}alter self{/i}) and appear as one of the living (as with {i}heartbeat{/i}).\n\nThe veil itself may change as part of the transformation becoming a hat, helmet, circlet, hair ornament or some other sort of headgear. This is not an illusion. The veil is actually changing shape.\n\nThis magic item is obviously intended to help intelligent undead infiltrate human society and for that it is most effective.\n\nHowever, it does have its limits. While it will defeat the first level detect undead, more powerful divination can defeat this magic item. {i}True seeing{/i} for example will show an undead for what he is.\n\n{b}CONSTRUCTION Requirements{/b} : Craft Wondrous Item, {i}alter self, heartbeat{/i} (see below) ; {b}Cost{/b} 7,200 gp" compset="Wondrous">
