  <thing id="ioWoWViFan" name="Vicious Fangs" description="These small wicked barbs are meant to be worn over the fangs of a vampire. Made of enchanted jagged iron with a small hollow channel that allows for the blood to flow freely, they greatly increase the damage done when the vampire drains blood from their victims. Wickedly devised, they do this without hindering feeding.\n\nThese fangs enhance a vampire&apos;s blood drain with 1d8 + Strength modifier damage plus 2 bleed damage in addition to the normal constitution loss.\n\nThese fangs can be worn or removed as a move action. While worn, the vampire cannot retract their fangs and appears as the blood-feasting undead they are to observers.\n\n{b}CONSTRUCTION Requirements{/b} : Craft Wondrous Item, {i}brow gasher{/i} ; {b}Cost{/b} 3,250 gp" compset="Wondrous" summary="1d4 Con and 1d8 + STR Mod plus 2 Bleed Damage">
